public static interface Util.TryFunction<T,R>
extends net.adamcin.oakpal.api.Fun.ThrowingFunction<T,R>
    Functional interface similar to Function, but which allows for throwing exceptions. Use with Util.composeTry(Function, Supplier, TryFunction, BiConsumer) to make suitable for flatMap.
